Module  : PM Keep Copy enabled by default
Version : 1.0.1
Author  : Maurice Makaay

This module will enable the "Keep a copy in my sent items" option by default
when writing a new private message.


Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "pm_keep_copy_by_default" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "PM Keep Copy enabled by default".

